幹道的狀況仍然十分惡劣，加上有個別巴士站的設施受到超強颱風山竹的破壞，基於員工及乘客的安全考慮，除1A（來往秀茂坪及旺角）、6、31、59M、60M、66M、68M、69M（只往荃灣）、71A、74X（往觀塘方向）、213M、234A、238M、265M（只往荃灣）、904、905、961、A31、E33、K12、K14、K17、K18、S1、S64提供有限度服務外，九巴及龍運其他日間巴士服務仍然需要暫停，直至另行通知。<br />\n<br />\n九巴及龍運仍會繼續與各政府部門緊密合作，務求盡快清理路面上的障礙物與及修復損毀的設施，及早恢復各巴士路線並提供有限度服務。<br />\n<br />\n*********************<br />\n<br />\n(16/9 20:45 最新消息) 九巴及龍運的外勤團隊經過初步的路面檢視及評估，基於安全理由，現宣佈暫停所有日間及通宵巴士服務，直至另行通知。<br />\n<br />\n乘客如有查詢，可致電九巴顧客服務熱線27454466。<br />\n<br />\n*********************<br />\n<br />\n颱風下，最快、最新的巴士服務消息，請查閱: <a href=\"http://www.kmb.hk/tc/news/press/archives/news201809162699.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.kmb.hk%2Ftc%2Fnews%2Fpress%2Farchives%2Fnews201809162699.html&d=jswbPQnabvIpAkxVJWlMC8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=3839d6d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.kmb.hk/tc/news/press/archives/news201809162699.html</a> 或APP1933有關颱風的交通安排消息。<br />\n<br />\n#九巴 #龍運 #KMB #LWB #颱風交通安排 #打風巴士服務 #請注意安全"},{"pid":"29bededc13437dbcf0c79679bdaa6fba8505e239","tid":823721,"uid":99627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T00:43:53.000Z","msg":"竟然有74x"},{"pid":"b2d7575b0fac62ff679e4b4ff7c155400b8bcf99","tid":823721,"uid":185836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T00:47:23.000Z","msg":"如果痴痴的等<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aadaaceabff1c68dbcf3c5a8ef4320a3286a597f","tid":823721,"uid":123296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T00:48:23.000Z","msg":"S64好似收咗皮<br />\n聽聞出唔到車"},{"pid":"3b63616bc95dd571df3b3f89f938c05f2f68e896","tid":823721,"uid":23993,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T00:49:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>我要番工呀</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f164683a